00:20:33,478 --> 00:20:36,174
- 莱昂・柯米副队长 - 笔，笔，笔
<i>Lieutenant Leon Comey. Pen, pen, pen.</i>

343
00:20:36,248 --> 00:20:38,512
记下来，C-O-M-E-Y
Write that down. C-O-M-E-Y.

344
00:20:39,351 --> 00:20:40,613
C-O-M-E-Y
<i>C- O-M-E-Y.</i>

345
00:20:40,685 --> 00:20:44,917
202-555-0167
202-555-0167.

346
00:20:44,990 --> 00:20:48,050
他会给你看一份非官方的…
He's gonna show you an off-the-record preview

347
00:20:48,126 --> 00:20:50,993
地铁站监控摄像头拍下的带子
of the security camera tapes from the Metro station.

348
00:20:51,062 --> 00:20:52,927
什么，你是说…你是不是说，现在？
What, you mean... Do you mean, like, now?

349
00:20:52,998 --> 00:20:54,989
是的，现在 不好意思，请问你是？
Yeah, like now. Sorry. Who am I calling?

350
00:20:55,133 --> 00:20:57,158
我找的是叫黛拉・弗雷娅的记者
I was trying to get Della Frye the reporter.

351
00:20:57,235 --> 00:21:00,102
哦，抱歉，我以为我在和今天早晨那个…
Gee, I'm sorry. I thought that I was talking to the guy

352
00:21:00,171 --> 00:21:01,695
不愿和我说话的人讲电话呢
who wouldn't give me the time of day this morning.

353
00:21:01,773 --> 00:21:06,870
听着，我只是想帮助你 好让你下次在网上大放厥词的时候…
Look, I am just trying to help you get a few facts in the mix

354
00:21:06,945 --> 00:21:09,573
至少有一点事实根据
next time you decide to upchuck online.

355
00:21:09,648 --> 00:21:10,876
什么？
What?

356
00:21:10,949 --> 00:21:11,938
<i>(LINE DISCONNECTS)</i>

357
00:21:16,121 --> 00:21:17,884
我才不干，我不干
I'm not doing it. I'm not.

358
00:21:26,564 --> 00:21:27,792
醒醒
DELLA: Wake up.

359
00:21:41,646 --> 00:21:44,513
有人知道514房在哪吗？
Does anybody know where Room 514 is?

360
00:21:46,284 --> 00:21:48,844
514A还是514B？
514A or 514B?

361
00:21:51,222 --> 00:21:53,656
这上面没写，有差吗？
It doesn't say. Is there a big difference?

362
00:21:53,725 --> 00:21:57,422
差别很大，你找的是统一行动组还是调查科？
Big enough. You looking for Uniform Squad or Investigation?

363
00:21:58,963 --> 00:22:01,693
我不知道 卡尔・麦卡弗雷让我来的
I don't know. Cal McAffrey sent me.

364
00:22:02,867 --> 00:22:04,334
为什么不早点说呢？
Why didn't you say so?

365
00:22:04,469 --> 00:22:05,936
你是卡尔的新助手？
You Cal's new assistant?

366
00:22:06,705 --> 00:22:08,036
不，不是
No, I'm not.

367
00:22:08,907 --> 00:22:10,204
嘿，能给我看一下吗？
Hey, can I see that?

368
00:22:12,010 --> 00:22:14,410
沿着走廊到底就是了
Yeah, it's right down the hallway here.

369
00:22:14,479 --> 00:22:15,468
谢谢你
Thank you.

370
00:22:15,547 --> 00:22:17,105
需要警方护送吗？
Like a police escort?

371
00:22:17,382 --> 00:22:19,043
不用了，我没问题 谢谢
No, I'm okay. Thank you.

372
00:22:19,117 --> 00:22:22,245
嘿，没关系的 我吃东西很快
Hey, no trouble. I'm just grabbing some dinner here real quick.

373
00:22:22,320 --> 00:22:24,788
你认识卡尔多久了？
So, how long have you known Cal?

374
00:22:24,856 --> 00:22:25,982
太久了
Too long.

375
00:22:31,663 --> 00:22:33,255
你的职位是什么？ 好的，警官
What's your title? Okay, Sergeant,

376
00:22:33,398 --> 00:22:34,990
我可以申请调查公共档案…
I can file a public records request

377
00:22:35,066 --> 00:22:36,795
然后查到信息
and get the information anyway.

378
00:22:40,033 --> 00:22:42,314
“华盛顿环球报：议员向死去的助手致哀”

379
00:22:44,476 --> 00:22:45,909
你什么都没查到？
You got nothing?

380
00:22:46,044 --> 00:22:47,511
没有
No.

381
00:22:48,146 --> 00:22:50,808
他们有56个摄像头，覆盖了地铁站台
They've got 56 cameras covering the track platforms.

382
00:22:50,882 --> 00:22:53,316
在整个系统中，有3个盲点
There are three blind spots in the entire system,

383
00:22:53,385 --> 00:22:55,580
而索尼娅・贝克就是在其中一个盲点丧命的
and Sonia Baker went down in one of them.

384
00:22:55,653 --> 00:22:57,382
卡尔，你有稿件要交给我吗？
You got copy for me, Cal?

385
00:22:57,455 --> 00:22:59,685
披萨递送员被枪击，你在做什么？
The shooting delivery guy, what are we doing?

386
00:22:59,758 --> 00:23:00,816
我正在写
I'm on it.

387
00:23:00,892 --> 00:23:02,917
我准备让马蒂拍一些受害者家人的照片
Well, I got Marty lined up to take some pictures of the family.

388
00:23:02,994 --> 00:23:05,019
如果需要的话，我可以派人陪他一起去
If you'd like, I can send somebody out there with him.

389
00:23:05,096 --> 00:23:06,996
他可以哭悼，你可以写具体的细节
He can do the crying, you can do the nuts and bolts.

390
00:23:07,065 --> 00:23:09,124
不，不必了，我正在写 今晚交给你
No. No need. I'm on it. You'll have it tonight.

391
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,667
你正在写
You're on it.

392
00:23:11,970 --> 00:23:13,699
好 你知道你必须要做什么吗？
(EXHALING) Okay. You know what you gotta do?

393
00:23:13,838 --> 00:23:15,567
打电话给莱昂，好吗？
Call Leon, all right?

394
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:17,540
逼他提供些细节
Just sort of push him for the details.

395
00:23:17,609 --> 00:23:19,076
再问他一些问题，就是…
Ask him a few more questions. You know...

396
00:23:19,144 --> 00:23:23,604
20年间有9起自杀事件，有5起意外死亡
Nine suicides in 20 years. There were five accidental deaths,

397
00:23:23,681 --> 00:23:25,046
3起是因为有人在列车进站之前
three from people trying to get their stuff

398
00:23:25,183 --> 00:23:26,548
在轨道上捡东西
off the tracks before the train came

399
00:23:26,618 --> 00:23:29,109
2起是因为精神病患推挤乘客掉入轨道
and two of the psycho-on-stranger pushing attacks.

400
00:23:29,187 --> 00:23:30,882
昨晚柯林斯是不是在你家过夜的？
Did Collins sleep at your place last night?

401
00:23:31,589 --> 00:23:33,216
- 什么？ - 嗯？
What? Hmm?

402
00:23:34,959 --> 00:23:37,689
我只是想确认事实
I was just trying to get my facts straight.

403
00:23:38,997 --> 00:23:41,227
抱歉，我是黛拉
(PHONE RINGING)

404
00:23:38,997 --> 00:23:41,227
Excuse me. Della here.

405
00:23:45,603 --> 00:23:47,093
稍等 他就在这
Yeah, just a sec. He's right here.

406
00:23:47,238 --> 00:23:48,728
等下，等下，等下
Hang on, hang on, hang on.

407
00:23:50,375 --> 00:23:52,536
是安妮・柯林斯的电话
It's Anne Collins.

408
00:23:55,613 --> 00:23:58,878
嘿，我现在不在自己的办公桌旁 能不能一会打给你？
Hey, I'm not at my desk at the moment. Can I call you back?

409
00:23:59,384 --> 00:24:00,544
好的
Yeah.

410
00:24:01,886 --> 00:24:04,946
查一下那两起推挤落轨事件
You know, look into the two psycho-on-stranger cases,

411
00:24:05,023 --> 00:24:07,218
看看有没有联系
see if anything correlates or anything connects.

412
00:24:07,325 --> 00:24:08,314
嗯
Mmm-hmm.

413
00:24:09,894 --> 00:24:11,452
(PHONE RINGING)

414
00:24:17,068 --> 00:24:18,797
- 喂？ - 嘿
<i>Hello? CAL... Hey.</i>

415
00:24:19,737 --> 00:24:21,227
- 你还好吗？ - 不
<i>You okay? No.</i>

416
00:24:22,474 --> 00:24:23,839
我的草坪上有很多狗仔队
There are paparazzi on my lawn,

417
00:24:23,908 --> 00:24:27,571
我猜我离上“美国周刊”不远了
<i>so I guess that entitles me to half off on Us Weekly.</i>

418
00:24:29,514 --> 00:24:30,776
我一直试着打你电话
I've been trying to call you.

419
00:24:31,983 --> 00:24:33,712
我关机了
I had my phone off.

420
00:24:34,486 --> 00:24:35,953
你和史蒂芬谈过了吗？
<i>You talk to Stephen yet?</i>

421
00:24:36,087 --> 00:24:37,554
还没
No.

422
00:24:39,657 --> 00:24:42,592
他们要我下去召开记者招待会
They want me to come down for a press conference.

423
00:24:42,660 --> 00:24:46,152
如果你不这么做，他们会把他送上刑场的
Well, you know if you don't, they're gonna toss him on the bonfire.

424
00:24:47,799 --> 00:24:49,460
我并没有很受伤的感觉
You know, I'm not that hurt.

425
00:24:49,601 --> 00:24:51,296
我甚至都不觉得太惊讶
I'm not even that surprised.

426
00:24:53,204 --> 00:24:55,502
只是实在是太丢人了
It's just so humiliating, you know.

427
00:24:55,807 --> 00:24:56,796
<i>(SIGHING)</i>

428
00:24:58,409 --> 00:24:59,433
告诉我你不知道她的存在
Tell me you didn't know about her.

429
00:24:59,511 --> 00:25:00,603
我不知道…
I didn't.

430
00:25:00,678 --> 00:25:02,669
我不知道她，知道吗？
I did not know about her, okay?

431
00:25:04,215 --> 00:25:05,409
我一会乘列车去你那
<i>I'll take the train down.</i>

432
00:25:06,551 --> 00:25:08,542
然后你能不能请我喝酒？
Will you buy me a drink after?

433
00:25:09,954 --> 00:25:13,754
没问题，嘿，给他打个电话，好吗？
Of course. Hey, just call him, all right?

434
00:25:13,825 --> 00:25:15,520
给史蒂芬打个电话
<i>Just call Stephen.</i>

435
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:17,355
谢谢
Thanks.

436
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:30,667
德尚・斯塔格
CAL: Deshaun Stagg.

437
00:25:30,808 --> 00:25:32,469
如果他们能把他的名字拼对就好了
Be nice if they could spell his name right.

438
00:25:32,544 --> 00:25:34,068
到现在还没有人来领他的东西
No one's even come to get his stuff yet.

439
00:25:34,212 --> 00:25:35,770
令人发指
It's appalling.

440
00:25:35,847 --> 00:25:37,712
这事从来不会发生在白人身上
Never happen to a white man.

441
00:25:37,782 --> 00:25:39,750
闭嘴 我没那个心情
Skip it. I'm not in the mood.

442
00:25:39,817 --> 00:25:41,580
怎么，不准谈爱，不准谈政治？
What, no love, no politics?

443
00:25:41,719 --> 00:25:43,482
那我们谈什么？
What are we gonna talk about?

444
00:25:43,555 --> 00:25:45,182
我们不谈 你赶紧离开这
We're not. You gotta get out of here

445
00:25:45,323 --> 00:25:46,984
免得我们都惹上麻烦
before we both get into trouble.

446
00:25:48,793 --> 00:25:50,988
他们说只有一个枪手，你怎么认为的？
They're saying it was only one shooter. What do you think?

447
00:25:51,062 --> 00:25:52,290
不清楚
No idea.

448
00:25:54,198 --> 00:25:55,756
毒品呢？
What about drugs?

449
00:25:55,900 --> 00:25:57,492
很有可能
It's a good bet.

450
00:25:58,269 --> 00:26:00,169
得了卡尔 别去碰那堆东西
Come on, Cal, leave that shit alone.

451
00:26:00,238 --> 00:26:02,866
眼睛闭起来，我只是在看他的手机
Close your eyes. I'm just checking out his cell phone.

452
00:26:04,442 --> 00:26:06,205
小心，这个钟点可能正是他们…
(SIGHING) Watch, this will be the moment they decide

453
00:26:06,344 --> 00:26:08,107
来把这些东西取走的时候
to come and pick all this shit up.

454
00:26:08,179 --> 00:26:10,272
那样的话你会怎么办？
Then what are you gonna do?

455
00:26:10,415 --> 00:26:12,542
写些文章，就可以帮我保住饭碗吗？
Write some articles, get me my job back?

456
00:26:12,617 --> 00:26:14,209
你知道我会这么做的
You know I will.

457
00:26:14,586 --> 00:26:15,814
卡尔？
Cal?

458
00:26:17,322 --> 00:26:20,155
卡尔，老天啊 如果杰克进来我怎么向他解释？
Cal, for Christ's sakes, what do I tell Jack if he walks in?

459
00:26:20,224 --> 00:26:22,192
不必解释，因为我搞定了
Nothing, 'cause I'm done.

460
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:28,498
下次我会给你一个拥抱，好吗？
I'll give you a hug next time, all right?

461
00:26:30,234 --> 00:26:31,292
再见
Bye.

462
00:26:37,909 --> 00:26:39,570
给我买瓶汽水？
Buy me a soda?

463
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,108
不要健怡的
Not diet.

464
00:26:54,892 --> 00:26:56,052
谢谢
Thanks.

465
00:27:00,531 --> 00:27:01,520
<i>(PHONE RINGING)</i>

466
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:04,593
哟，哟，如果想给基皮留言
<i>Yo, yo, if you want to leave a message for Kippy,</i>

467
00:27:04,669 --> 00:27:06,159
务必留下号码，好吗？
<i>make sure you leave your number, all right?</i>

468
00:27:06,237 --> 00:27:08,569
那样我就你能回打给你，回头见
<i>That way I can call you back. Later for you.</i>

469
00:27:10,975 --> 00:27:13,443
对不起，您所拨打的电话…
<i>AUTOMATED OPERATOR... We're sorry. Your call cannot be...</i>

470
00:27:15,513 --> 00:27:16,502
<i>(PHONE RINGING)</i>

471
00:27:17,749 --> 00:27:18,977
哟，你谁？
<i>MAN... Yo, who this?</i>

472
00:27:19,050 --> 00:27:20,677
我，老兄 你谁？
It's me, man. Who that?

473
00:27:20,752 --> 00:27:23,619
我谁？娘的，是你自己把来电显示屏蔽的！
<i>Me who? Bitch, you the one got your number blocked!</i>

474
00:27:23,688 --> 00:27:26,987
- 不要跟我耍花招，兄弟 - 我是德尚，拜托
Don't be fronting me, man. It's Deshaun. Come on.

475
00:27:27,058 --> 00:27:28,150
- 少来 - 你在哪里？
<i>No. Where you at?</i>

476
00:27:28,226 --> 00:27:30,160
到底是谁给了你我的号码，蠢人？
<i>Who the hell gave you my number, fool?</i>

477
00:27:30,228 --> 00:27:31,752
我刚在和基皮通电话
I was just talking to Kippy.

478
00:27:31,829 --> 00:27:33,456
- 基皮？ - 基皮啊，兄弟
<i>Skippy? Kippy, man.</i>

479
00:27:33,531 --> 00:27:34,657
一点也不好玩，耍花招
<i>This shit ain't funny, trick.</i>

480
00:27:45,309 --> 00:27:46,901
嗨，我是索尼娅・贝克
<i>Hi. You've reached Sonia Baker.</i>

481
00:27:46,978 --> 00:27:48,309
我现在无法接听你的电话
<i>I can't take your call right now,</i>

482
00:27:48,379 --> 00:27:49,778
但是如果你留下姓名和号码
<i>but if you leave your name, number,</i>

483
00:27:49,847 --> 00:27:53,044
以及你打电话的时间 我一定会回打给你，谢谢
<i>and the time you called, I'll be sure to get back to you. Thanks.</i>

484
00:28:04,829 --> 00:28:06,421
嗨，我是索尼娅・贝克
<i>Hi. You've reached Sonia Baker.</i>

485
00:28:06,497 --> 00:28:07,862
我现在无法接听你的电话
<i>I can't take your call right now,</i>

486
00:28:07,999 --> 00:28:09,398
但是如果你留下姓名和号码
<i>but if you leave your name, number,</i>

487
00:28:09,467 --> 00:28:12,561
以及你打电话的时间 我一定会回打给你，谢谢
<i>and the time you called, I'll be sure to get back to you. Thanks.</i>

488
00:28:19,410 --> 00:28:20,741
抱歉
Excuse me.

489
00:28:24,015 --> 00:28:25,380
索尼娅・贝克
Sonia Baker.

490
00:28:26,050 --> 00:28:27,984
我们有关于她吸毒的消息吗？
We got any kind of drug angle on her?

491
00:28:28,052 --> 00:28:30,418
她有被拘捕或者进过戒毒所之类吗？
She ever arrested or rehabbed or anything like that?

492
00:28:30,488 --> 00:28:32,319
- 是谁问的？ - 我
Who's asking? Me.

493
00:28:32,824 --> 00:28:34,849
这报道不是你负责的
You're not on the story.

494
00:28:34,926 --> 00:28:36,826
是我让你去看地铁录像带的，不是吗？
I gave you the Metro tapes idea, right?

495
00:28:37,328 --> 00:28:38,727
没错
Yeah.

496
00:28:39,664 --> 00:28:43,191
你是想把她名声毁坏殆尽吗？
So are you trying to ruin what's left of her reputation?

497
00:28:44,135 --> 00:28:46,103
你这么做是不是为了柯林斯？
Are you doing this for Collins?

498
00:28:46,237 --> 00:28:48,205
一点索尼娅的背景调查？
A little context on Sonia?

499
00:28:50,308 --> 00:28:52,242
你真会开玩笑
You gotta be kidding.

500
00:29:03,788 --> 00:29:04,982
嘿，莫里斯
Hey, Maurice.

501
00:29:05,056 --> 00:29:07,422
嘿，卡尔，和平常一样吗？
Hey, Cal, you getting your regular?

502
00:29:07,492 --> 00:29:08,481
是的
Yeah.

503
00:29:08,559 --> 00:29:09,924
没问题，嘿，小杰！
Sure. Hey, Jay!

504
00:29:10,428 --> 00:29:15,365
一个辣干酪汉堡，一份辣干酪薯条 还有一份辣香肠
I need a chili cheeseburger, a chili cheese fry, and a chili half-smoke.

505
00:29:15,433 --> 00:29:17,264
我正在做汉堡！
I got the burger on!

506
00:29:18,770 --> 00:29:20,567
有人给你点单了吗？
Anybody get you yet?

507
00:29:25,181 --> 00:29:27,611
“本氏餐馆免费就餐名单： 只有比尔・科斯比”

508
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:30,975
好的 你饿了，对吗？
All right. You're a hungry man, eh?

509
00:29:31,048 --> 00:29:32,072
是的
Yeah.

510
00:29:32,150 --> 00:29:33,674
情况怎么样，黑皮？
How's it going, Happy?

511
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:58,338
想再要一瓶汽水的话，大可不必这样做
That's a long way to go for another soda.

512
00:30:00,711 --> 00:30:04,647
你想买德尚最后一次偷的包里的东西吗？
