Don't they do background checks on the Hill?

582
00:35:20,231 --> 00:35:22,222
她替柯林斯写了有关银行规范…
DELLA: She wrote position papers for Collins

583
00:35:22,366 --> 00:35:24,391
和证券交易委员会的意见书
about bank regulations and the SEC.

584
00:35:24,468 --> 00:35:26,402
