I mean, a lot of people thought she was a star.

585
00:35:26,470 --> 00:35:30,406
同时她还是针对“尖兵集团”的听证会的 首席研究员
She was also the lead researcher on the PointCorp hearings.

586
00:35:31,175 --> 00:35:32,335
那又怎样？
CAMERON: So?

587
00:35:34,278 --> 00:35:38,078
史蒂芬会让那些人损失很多钱
Stephen represents the loss of a lot of money for those guys.

588
00:35:39,750 --> 00:35:43,208
听着，如果这些一切只是…
Look, what if all of this is just an attempt

589
00:35:43,287 --> 00:35:45,050
为了排挤史蒂芬・柯林斯，会怎样？
to marginalize Stephen Collins?

590
00:35:46,690 --> 00:35:48,487
你能说出这样的话，一定很爱他，对吧？
CAMERON: You've gotta love him for it, haven't you?

591
00:35:48,559 --> 00:35:51,790
给他24小时和一具小巷里的尸体
I mean, you give him 24 hours, body in the alley,

592
00:35:51,862 --> 00:35:53,523
这个老头就能编出一个…
and this geezer will turn it into

593
00:35:53,664 --> 00:35:55,325
有模有样的集团阴谋
a full-blown corporate conspiracy.

594
00:35:55,399 --> 00:35:56,525
你看不到关联吗？
You don't see any connection?

595
00:35:56,667 --> 00:35:57,827
看不到
No.

596
00:35:58,369 --> 00:36:00,530
那好吧，我们现在整理一下我们知道的情报 好吗？
All right. Let's go through what we know, okay?

597
00:36:00,604 --> 00:36:03,402
那个尾随索尼娅・贝克的男人
The guy that was stalking Sonia Baker,

598
00:36:03,541 --> 00:36:06,339
枪杀了德尚・斯塔格 和弗农・桑杜
he shot Deshaun Stagg and Vernon Sando.

599
00:36:07,912 --> 00:36:11,678
德尚・斯塔格没有固定居所 他偷了一个文件包
Deshaun Stagg, of no fixed abode, he boosts a briefcase.

600
00:36:11,749 --> 00:36:14,411
那个文件包里装着这些照片
Now, in that briefcase are these photographs,

601
00:36:14,485 --> 00:36:18,478
据知线人所说 还装着一小包奇怪的子弹
and according to our source, a little baggie of weird bullets.

602
00:36:19,690 --> 00:36:21,021
地铁警局的弹道分析结果显示
Metro PD ballistics tell me

603
00:36:21,091 --> 00:36:24,857
犯罪现场的弹壳是被二次使用的 我们无法追踪
the casings at the crime scene were reloads, untraceable.

604
00:36:25,729 --> 00:36:30,029
子弹比普通商店里买的重两倍， 是手动发射的
The slugs were hand cast at twice the weight of store-bought bullets,

605
00:36:30,868 --> 00:36:32,358
是扩散型的
X'ed for expansion.

606
00:36:32,436 --> 00:36:35,166
也就是说杀手想置人于死地
So that means that the shooter intended to kill.

607
00:36:36,807 --> 00:36:39,002
斯塔格和桑杜都连挨两枪
Stagg and Sando were both double-tapped,

608
00:36:39,076 --> 00:36:41,704
一颗子弹在脊椎，另一颗在头部 这是职业杀手的做法
one bullet in the spine, one in the head. That is the mark of a pro,

609
00:36:41,779 --> 00:36:44,771
或者至少也是当过兵的
or at the very least, somebody with a military background,

610
00:36:44,882 --> 00:36:46,873
