perhaps even Special Forces.

611
00:36:47,418 --> 00:36:53,414
“尖兵集团”的建立者和雇员 全都是当过兵的人
PointCorp founded by, staffed by 100./. Ex-military.

612
00:36:56,093 --> 00:36:58,653
