936
00:53:30,787 --> 00:53:32,118
多米尼克
Dominic.

937
00:53:32,322 --> 00:53:34,790
嘿，麦克，是卡尔 你发现了什么？
Hey, Michael, it's Cal. So what did you find out?

938
00:53:35,491 --> 00:53:36,480
<i>(KNOCKING AT DOOR)</i>

939
00:53:38,094 --> 00:53:40,289
你好，斯塔勒先生？ 什么事？
<i>DELLA... Hi. Mr. Statler? STATLER... Yes?</i>

940
00:53:40,363 --> 00:53:41,591
我是环球报的记者
<i>Yes, I'm from the Globe.</i>

941
00:53:41,664 --> 00:53:43,894
我在写一篇关于索尼娅・贝克之死的文章
I'm writing an article on the death of Sonia Baker,

942
00:53:43,967 --> 00:53:45,491
我想…
and I just wanted to...

943
00:53:46,069 --> 00:53:47,764
他曾在“尖兵集团”当高层？
And he was, like, high up in PointCorp?

944
00:53:48,571 --> 00:53:51,335
你好，我是华盛顿环球报的黛拉・弗雷娅
<i>Hi. Della Frye from the Washington Globe.</i>

945
00:53:51,808 --> 00:53:53,935
我…我能不能和你谈谈？ 请别…
I... Could I speak to you? Please don't...

