he campaigns against the expansion,

973
00:55:20,663 --> 00:55:22,358
接着就在一起离奇的车祸中丧生
and then he dies in a freak car accident.

974
00:55:22,432 --> 00:55:24,662
好的，“离奇的车祸”是什么意思？
CAL: All right, what does "freak car accident" mean?

975
00:55:24,734 --> 00:55:26,531
大白天…他在空旷的马路上开车
Middle of the day... He's driving on the open road...

976
00:55:26,602 --> 00:55:27,660
