00:55:40,450 --> 00:55:42,941
的地铁监视录像
in the Metro security footage, right?

983
00:55:43,019 --> 00:55:47,854
她进入盲点20分钟后，这个人出现了
And 20 seconds after she went into the blind spot, this guy appears.

984
00:55:48,524 --> 00:55:49,752
知道吗？
Okay?

985
00:55:52,595 --> 00:55:55,928
我昨晚在医院看到他了
I think that I saw him last night at the hospital.

986
00:56:02,305 --> 00:56:03,932
你确定吗？
Are you sure?

987
00:56:17,987 --> 00:56:19,579
麦克，我是卡尔
Michael, it's Cal.

988
00:56:19,655 --> 00:56:23,386
你说的“尖兵集团”的内部人员 我现在要见他
Your PointCorp insider, I need to meet him, now.

989
00:56:53,856 --> 00:56:55,448
你要知道
I want you to know something.

990
00:56:55,591 --> 00:56:57,218
我爱祖国
I love my country.

991
00:56:57,293 --> 00:56:58,419
我爱军队
I love the military.

992
00:56:58,561 --> 00:56:59,687
