Understand.

998
00:57:09,439 --> 00:57:11,100
我在找一个人
CAL: I'm looking for a guy that PointCorp

999
00:57:11,240 --> 00:57:12,901
他参加了“尖兵集团”的隐蔽军事行动
are using on a covert operation.

1000
00:57:12,975 --> 00:57:14,340
官方完全否认
Total deniability.

1001
00:57:14,410 --> 00:57:16,571
我们在国防部共同的朋友觉得…
Our mutual friend at DOD thought

1002
00:57:16,712 --> 00:57:18,907
你有可能能帮助我们找到他
you might be able to help us find him.

1003
00:57:20,249 --> 00:57:22,911
我不知道，我会查一下
I don't know. I'll check it out.

1004
00:57:25,688 --> 00:57:28,851
你是怎么理解“尖兵集团”的口号的？
So, what's your understanding of the PointCorp MO?

1005
00:57:28,925 --> 00:57:30,324
他们的口号？
Their MO?

1006
00:57:30,393 --> 00:57:32,122
他们随心所欲
They do whatever the hell they want.

1007
00:57:32,595 --> 00:57:34,620
这些军人不受束缚
These soldiers are answerable to no one.

1008
00:57:34,764 --> 00:57:36,823
