1011
00:57:41,904 --> 00:57:44,338
委员会的主席，史蒂芬・柯林斯…
So, the head of the committee there, Stephen Collins...

1012
00:57:44,407 --> 00:57:45,567
他完蛋了
He's finished.

1013
00:57:45,641 --> 00:57:47,973
他们会不断攻击他直到他离职
They'll just keep knocking him down until he goes away.

1014
00:57:48,044 --> 00:57:49,909
你知道他的所做所为造成了多大的威胁吗？
Do you have any idea what he's threatening here?

1015
00:57:49,979 --> 00:57:53,073
公司每年赚三、四百亿
This is $30 or $40 billion annually.

1016
00:57:53,149 --> 00:57:54,776
上帝都会愤怒的数字
That's wrath of God money.

1017
00:57:54,851 --> 00:57:57,149
听证会上说的是三、四十亿
The hearings are saying 3 or 4.

1018
00:57:57,220 --> 00:57:59,711
那是海外的，真正让尖兵集团赚大钱的…
Overseas. The real money is what PointCorp

1019
00:57:59,856 --> 00:58:02,381
是国内的军事行动
stands to make in its domestic operations.

1020
00:58:02,825 --> 00:58:04,725
我以为他们不在国内行动
I wasn't aware that they had any.

1021
00:58:04,794 --> 00:58:08,958
卡特里娜飓风过后是谁被派去控制局面？ 是我们
Who was sent in for crowd control after Hurricane Katrina? Us.

1022
00:58:09,465 --> 00:58:11,262
私营安保承包商被授权…
Private security contractors deputized

1023
00:58:11,400 --> 00:58:13,231
射击美国民众
to shoot at American citizens.

1024
00:58:14,070 --> 00:58:17,369
芝加哥警察的新审问技巧是谁训练出来的？
<i>Who's training Chicago police on new interrogation techniques?</i>

1025
00:58:18,007 --> 00:58:20,703
很快，“尖兵集团”就会取代国家安全委员会
Soon, PointCorp will take over from the NSA

1026
00:58:20,843 --> 00:58:23,573
监听电话，有关恐怖分子资料，所有的一切
on phone taps, terrorist databases, all of it.

1027
00:58:24,347 --> 00:58:26,247
这是国内情报策略的…
It's a fundamental restructuring

1028
00:58:26,315 --> 00:58:28,374
根本重组
of domestic intelligence policy.

1029
00:58:29,151 --> 00:58:32,018
是国土安全的民营私有化
It is the privatization of Homeland Security.

1030
00:58:32,088 --> 00:58:34,522
数以亿计的美元
Billions and billions of dollars.

1031
00:58:34,857 --> 00:58:37,325
你真的认为他们会为了一个…
Now you really think they're gonna forfeit all that

1032
00:58:37,393 --> 00:58:39,327
从宾夕法尼亚州第七选区来的英雄…
<i>because some hero from the seventh district</i>

1033
00:58:39,462 --> 00:58:41,396
放弃所有这一切吗？
<i>of Pennsylvania thinks that they should?</i>

1034
00:58:41,464 --> 00:58:42,453
嘿
Hey.

1035
00:58:44,100 --> 00:58:47,126
我刚联系到了一个曾经在 “尖兵集团”工作的员工
<i>CAL... I just got told by a former PointCorp employee</i>

1036
00:58:47,203 --> 00:58:49,831
他告诉我他们打算垄断国家安全工作
<i>that they have a plan to monopolize domestic security</i>

1037
00:58:49,906 --> 00:58:51,601
每年可赚四百亿
<i>that's worth about $40 billion a year.</i>

1038
00:58:51,741 --> 00:58:53,436
是真的吗？
<i>Is that true?</i>

1039
00:58:53,509 --> 00:58:55,306
- 没错 - 怎么做的？
<i>STEPHEN... Yes. CAL... How?</i>

1040
00:58:55,378 --> 00:58:57,903
你不能把所有我告诉你的事情与我关联起来
You cannot connect anything that I tell you back to me.

1041
00:58:57,980 --> 00:58:59,174
- 你知道吗？ - 当然
You understand? Of course.

1042
00:58:59,248 --> 00:59:00,237
好吧
Okay.

1043
00:59:01,384 --> 00:59:04,581
去年有47家公司竞标国土安全合约
Last year, 47 companies bid on major Homeland Security contracts.

1044
00:59:04,654 --> 00:59:07,316
其中有16家公司夺标
Of those, 16 companies were granted the bids.

1045
00:59:07,390 --> 00:59:11,451
在夺标的公司中，14家公司有联系
Of those, I could make connections between 14 companies,

1046
00:59:11,527 --> 00:59:13,495
我说的不是…
and I'm not just talking about someone leaving one company

1047
00:59:13,563 --> 00:59:14,587
公司间的人员流动
and go work for another.

1048
00:59:14,664 --> 00:59:16,495
我说的是共同的银行帐户
I'm talking about shared banking practices.

1049
00:59:16,632 --> 00:59:18,463
说的是一致的阴谋
I'm talking about collusive behavior.

1050
00:59:18,534 --> 00:59:20,866
我的观点就是 到最后…
Now, my belief is, when all's said and done

1051
00:59:21,003 --> 00:59:23,335
把面纱揭开…
and when the veil is pulled away,

1052
00:59:23,406 --> 00:59:26,534
你看到的不是14家不同的公司
you will not see 14 individual companies.

1053
00:59:27,176 --> 00:59:31,010
而是一家公司，明白吗?
You will see one company. You understand?

1054
00:59:32,381 --> 00:59:33,575
你一直在四处打探
And you've been digging around

1055
00:59:33,716 --> 00:59:34,910
试图弄清他们之间的关系
trying to make those connections clear.

1056
00:59:34,984 --> 00:59:36,815
是的，没错
Yeah. That's right.

1057
00:59:38,020 --> 00:59:40,045
索尼娅也参与其中？
And Sonia was working on that?

1058
00:59:40,122 --> 00:59:41,987
她是首席研究员
She was my lead researcher.

1059
00:59:42,124 --> 00:59:44,024
她参与了所有事情
She was involved in everything we did.

1060
00:59:44,093 --> 00:59:46,687
他们无论如何不会放过你的，史蒂芬
They're gonna get you, Stephen, one way or another.

1061
00:59:46,762 --> 00:59:50,323
他们有四百亿个好理由除掉你
They got 40 billion good reasons to want you out of the way.

1062
00:59:50,399 --> 00:59:51,764
你必须发表正式申明
You gotta go on the record.

1063
00:59:51,901 --> 00:59:53,266
将焦点转向他们
Swing the spotlight back on them.

1064
00:59:53,336 --> 00:59:55,827
你得保护自己，兄弟
You gotta protect yourself, man.

1065
00:59:57,106 --> 01:00:00,769
你要帮我找能把索尼娅的死和“尖兵集团”…
You go out there and find me evidence

1066
01:00:01,410 --> 01:00:04,174
联系起来的证据
linking Sonia's death to PointCorp.

1067
01:00:05,948 --> 01:00:08,280
我会发表正式申明
I will go on the record.

1068
01:00:08,417 --> 01:00:10,749
我会将这件事公诸于众
I will shout this thing from the rooftops.

1069
01:00:11,754 --> 01:00:13,312
我没问题
I can do that.

1070
01:00:17,293 --> 01:00:20,956
好了，我要进去了，保持联系
All right. I gotta get back. I'll be in touch.

1071
01:00:21,030 --> 01:00:22,964
- 史蒂芬 - 什么事？
Stephen. Yeah?

1072
01:00:23,599 --> 01:00:25,362
一切小心
Just watch your back.

1073
01:00:25,501 --> 01:00:27,264
你也是
You, too.

1074
01:00:36,512 --> 01:00:38,275
嗨，朗达在这吗？
Hi. Is Rhonda here?

1075
01:00:38,414 --> 01:00:40,177
在，她就在那边
Yeah, she's just right over there.

1076
01:00:40,983 --> 01:00:41,972
哦
<i>(SINGING) Whoa</i>

1077
01:00:42,118 --> 01:00:44,313
我踏着阳光前行
<i>I'm walking on sunshine</i>

1078
01:00:44,654 --> 01:00:46,349
哦
<i>Whoa</i>

1079
01:00:46,489 --> 01:00:49,049
我踏着阳光前行
<i>I'm walking on sunshine</i>

1080
01:00:49,125 --> 01:00:50,717
