<i>Whoa</i>

1081
01:00:50,960 --> 01:00:52,825
感觉如此美妙
<i>And don't it feel good</i>

1082
01:00:53,029 --> 01:00:54,018
耶！
Yeah!

1083
01:00:54,230 --> 01:00:57,597
卡尔 你不会相信索尼娅的前舍友跟我说了什么的
DELLA: Cal, you're not gonna believe what Sonia's old roommate just told me.

1084
01:00:58,567 --> 01:01:00,865
你说对了 我一个字也不相信
You're right. I don't believe a word of it.

1085
01:01:00,936 --> 01:01:03,097
你没有确证的事实，没有目击证人
You got no corroboration, no independent witness,

1086
01:01:03,172 --> 01:01:05,265
而且很显然她缺钱，她的动机很明显
and she obviously has a financial motivation.

1087
01:01:05,341 --> 01:01:07,332
索尼娅・贝克的舍友声明…
We've got Sonia Baker's roommate claiming

1088
01:01:07,410 --> 01:01:09,378
她和史蒂芬・柯林斯玩三角关系
she had a threesome with Stephen Collins,

1089
01:01:09,445 --> 01:01:10,537
你要忽视这一点吗？
and you want to ignore that?

1090
01:01:10,613 --> 01:01:13,241
我不是要忽视，我只说要考虑
I am not saying ignore it. I am saying consider it.

1091
01:01:13,315 --> 01:01:15,249
考虑这会对我们所掌握的其他信息 产生什么样的影响
Consider how it impacts everything else we have,

1092
01:01:15,317 --> 01:01:17,251
考虑她有可能满嘴胡话
and consider that she is full of shit!

1093
01:01:17,319 --> 01:01:19,617
没错，但是， 卡尔 她还说
Yeah, but, Cal, she's also saying

1094
01:01:19,689 --> 01:01:23,056
史蒂芬帮索尼娅还了四万美元的卡账
that Stephen paid off Sonia's $40,000 credit card debt.

1095
01:01:23,125 --> 01:01:24,456
那足以写篇文章
That is a story.

1096
01:01:24,527 --> 01:01:26,358
这消息必须要上头版
Somebody's gonna put that on the front page.

1097
01:01:26,429 --> 01:01:29,159
好吧，这样做对吗？
Okay, is that the right thing to do?

1098
01:01:29,231 --> 01:01:32,598
听着，那部分是你负责的，是你的独家新闻
Look, it's your half of the story. It's your scoop.

1099
01:01:32,668 --> 01:01:35,296
由你自己决定，随你怎么做
Your decision. Do whatever you want.

1100
01:01:44,980 --> 01:01:47,847
但是我知道我和史蒂芬…
<i>ANNE... But I do know that Stephen and I</i>

1101
01:01:47,983 --> 01:01:50,850
一起经历了很多…
<i>have been through far too much together</i>

1102
01:01:50,920 --> 01:01:54,617
才走到今天，这一刻将决定成败
<i>to make this one moment the thing that defines us forever.</i>

1103
01:01:54,690 --> 01:01:55,987
政治前途…
<i>REPORTER... The political future...</i>

1104
01:02:11,240 --> 01:02:12,935
我试过给你打电话
I tried to call.

1105
01:02:13,442 --> 01:02:17,742
我打了12次，但是每次都挂掉了
I mean, I actually did call about 12 times, but I hung up every time.

1106
01:02:18,380 --> 01:02:21,281
你来我很高兴
Well, you know, I'm glad you dropped by,

1107
01:02:22,118 --> 01:02:24,882
因为我一直想和你谈谈
'cause I've been wanting to talk to you.

1108
01:02:28,491 --> 01:02:31,051
记得你从柏林洪堡带来的那个女孩吗？
Remember you brought that girl from Humboldt?

1109
01:02:31,127 --> 01:02:32,526
索蕾尔，还是叫什么的
Soleil, or whatever her name was.

1110
01:02:32,595 --> 01:02:33,687
露娜
Luna.

1111
01:02:33,763 --> 01:02:36,391
露娜，没错
Luna. That's right.

1112
01:02:36,954 --> 01:02:40,219
当时整个过程你们俩都被吓僵了
And you two were stoned the whole time.

1113
01:02:40,290 --> 01:02:41,314
对
Yep.

1114
01:02:41,391 --> 01:02:43,291
你成功把船弄翻了，弄丢所有的东西
You managed to flip the boat, and we lost everything.

1115
01:02:43,360 --> 01:02:44,418
剩下的路程都是靠走的…
We had to walk the rest of the way...

1116
01:02:44,494 --> 01:02:45,586
我们把船弄翻了？
We flipped the boat?

1117
01:02:45,662 --> 01:02:46,720
你弄翻了
You did.

1118
01:02:47,431 --> 01:02:49,058
那的确是次冒险
It was an adventure.

1119
01:02:49,666 --> 01:02:51,293
你一直都在冒险
That's what you kept saying.

1120
01:02:51,835 --> 01:02:52,893
爱尔兰酒
Irish wine.

1121
01:02:53,036 --> 01:02:54,128
威士忌？
Whiskey?

1122
01:02:55,539 --> 01:02:57,268
- 干杯 - 干杯（爱尔兰语）
<i>Cheers. Sláinte.</i>

1123
01:03:03,080 --> 01:03:04,604
- 那… - 那…
So... So...

1124
01:03:06,483 --> 01:03:07,950
- 我一直… - 我想问问…
I've been... I wanted to ask...

1125
01:03:08,018 --> 01:03:09,849
- 抱歉 - 你先说吧
Sorry. You first.

1126
01:03:11,922 --> 01:03:13,617
我在想…
I was wondering,

1127
01:03:16,393 --> 01:03:21,160
你觉得史蒂芬能瞒着你凑到4万美金吗？
do you think Stephen could have pulled together $40,000 without you knowing?

1128
01:03:21,231 --> 01:03:22,357
什么？
What?

1129
01:03:22,432 --> 01:03:23,626
这消息可能令人震惊
Well, it's a story that might break

1130
01:03:23,700 --> 01:03:26,191
它会直指史蒂芬正在做一些…
that basically accuses Stephen of doing something

1131
01:03:26,270 --> 01:03:30,639
须要直接调用大量现金的行为
that would require his having access to a large amount of cash.

1132
01:03:30,707 --> 01:03:33,540
我在想，他会这么做吗？
I was just wondering, could he do that?

1133
01:03:33,610 --> 01:03:34,838
震惊的消息？
A story that might break?

1134
01:03:34,912 --> 01:03:36,777
你是说和你有关的事情？
You mean something that you're involved in?

1135
01:03:36,847 --> 01:03:38,678
- 间接有关 - 你在做什么？
Indirectly. What are you doing?

1136
01:03:38,749 --> 01:03:41,479
我在努力帮助史蒂芬 努力保护你
I'm trying to help Stephen. I'm trying to protect you.

1137
01:03:42,019 --> 01:03:43,577
胡扯！
Bullshit!

1138
01:03:44,354 --> 01:03:45,343
(SIGHS)

1139
01:03:45,856 --> 01:03:47,847
你总是这样
You always do this.

1140
01:03:49,526 --> 01:03:52,723
有时候我觉得我们大家都约好了似的
Sometimes I feel like we all made this deal,

1141
01:03:52,796 --> 01:03:56,857
然后发现事情对你和史蒂芬都有好处 但对我不是
and it works out great for you and Stephen, and not for me.

1142
01:03:56,934 --> 01:03:58,333
然后等我们其他人发现之后…
And instead of us just figuring it out,

1143
01:03:58,402 --> 01:04:02,600
你们俩就像什么也没发生一样信步离开
you guys are just fine walking around as if nothing ever happened.

1144
01:04:08,211 --> 01:04:09,473
好吧
Okay.

1145
01:04:13,216 --> 01:04:15,047
好吧，我们再来一次
Okay, let's start over.

1146
01:04:15,118 --> 01:04:16,517
我来这是为了和你谈谈…
I come here to tell you that I'm thinking

1147
01:04:16,586 --> 01:04:17,917
我想结束这段婚姻的事情
about walking away from my marriage,

1148
01:04:17,988 --> 01:04:19,751
而你说的什么？
and you say what?

1149
01:04:20,624 --> 01:04:24,060
我说太晚了 时过境迁了
I say it's too late. We're way past this.

1150
01:04:25,128 --> 01:04:26,857
你作出了你的选择
You made your choice.

1151
01:04:26,930 --> 01:04:28,363
那是因为你不肯行动
Because you wouldn't step up.

1152
01:04:28,432 --> 01:04:30,229
你到底在想什么？
(STAMMERING) What do you mean?

1153
01:04:31,468 --> 01:04:34,198
那时不肯，现在不肯，大学时不肯
Not then, not now, not in college.

1154
01:04:35,772 --> 01:04:37,706
我是说，你现在在要求我…
I'm saying that you're asking me

1155
01:04:37,841 --> 01:04:39,775
给你一些不现实的东西
for something that's not real.

1156
01:04:40,510 --> 01:04:42,501
这就是我的意思
That's what I'm saying.

1157
01:04:44,848 --> 01:04:46,372
安妮…
(SIGHS) Annie...

1158
01:04:58,495 --> 01:05:01,020
我们正在按揭两处房产
We have two mortgages.

1159
01:05:01,098 --> 01:05:03,259
在维吉尼亚有
We have the place in Virginia.

1160
01:05:03,400 --> 01:05:05,595
这边的公寓也是
We've got the apartment here.

1161
01:05:05,669 --> 01:05:07,034
可以说，我们用上了我们的一切
Basically, we spend everything we make,

1162
01:05:07,104 --> 01:05:10,938
所以，史蒂芬不可能在我不知情的情况下…
so there's no way Stephen could have given anyone $40,000

1163
01:05:11,008 --> 01:05:13,306
给任何人4万美金
without me knowing about it.

1164
01:05:15,612 --> 01:05:17,512
- 安妮… - 没关系
Annie... It's okay.

1165
01:05:20,384 --> 01:05:22,375
我现在是个线人
Now I'm just a source,

1166
01:05:23,620 --> 01:05:25,713
所以别有压力
so the pressure's off.

1167
01:05:35,132 --> 01:05:36,394
