1169
01:05:57,754 --> 01:06:00,154
- 喂？ - 那漂亮的金发女人是谁，卡尔？
<i>Hello? MAN ON PHONE... Who's the great-Iooking blonde, Cal?</i>

1170
01:06:01,458 --> 01:06:02,618
你是谁？
Who's this?

1171
01:06:02,692 --> 01:06:04,125
在街对面
<i>Across the street.</i>

1172
01:06:19,076 --> 01:06:21,101
我喜欢你的造型
I like your style, man.

1173
01:06:22,412 --> 01:06:23,572
我有消息给你
I got something for you.

1174
01:06:23,647 --> 01:06:25,547
你就不能走前门？
And you couldn't just ring the doorbell?

1175
01:06:26,416 --> 01:06:28,247
谨慎些好
Precautions.

1176
01:06:28,318 --> 01:06:32,152
照片里那人，我到处问过了 绝对是个小人物
The guy in the photo, I asked around. He's definitely a grunt.

1177
01:06:32,422 --> 01:06:35,823
我朋友过去常在保安工作的商业演出中 见到他
Buddy of mine used to see him at security trade shows.

1178
01:06:35,892 --> 01:06:37,655
但从来不知道名字
Never knew his name,

1179
01:06:37,727 --> 01:06:40,696
但他为一位叫弗雷德・苏莫斯的老前辈工作
but he worked for an old-timer called Fred Summers.

1180
01:06:40,764 --> 01:06:43,028
做些类似安装警报系统的工作
Does alarm installations, shit like that.

1181
01:06:43,800 --> 01:06:45,893
这是弗雷德的地址
Here's Fred's address.

1182
01:06:46,369 --> 01:06:47,996
